    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <strong>TOTAL RELOAD</strong> 中，您必须学会“用电线思考”，换句话说，要明白通过临时为各种物体供电，您可以到达以前无法到达的地方。很难从视频中感受到这款游戏机制的全部深度，因此我们发布了一个演示，其中包含完整版游戏中 20% 的地点。在演示版本中，您将能够充分体验“用电线思考”的含义，并学习如何与一些设备交互：量子传输器、能量发射器、传感器网格、能量立方体、能量转换器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您将能够从玩完演示版的地方开始玩完整版游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135100/extras/3911ebf875875f8072e8156ec6f84e7b.poster.avif?t=1762011663\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135100/extras/3911ebf875875f8072e8156ec6f84e7b.webm?t=1762011663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135100/extras/3911ebf875875f8072e8156ec6f84e7b.mp4?t=1762011663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135100/extras/af19e6c9db4a9a84ba8b5ed08c6958d6.poster.avif?t=1762011663\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135100/extras/af19e6c9db4a9a84ba8b5ed08c6958d6.webm?t=1762011663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135100/extras/af19e6c9db4a9a84ba8b5ed08c6958d6.mp4?t=1762011663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
